  <description><![CDATA[<p>As stated in the name, Nozawa View Hotel really gives you a beautiful view of <a data-udi="umb://document/cb5fe8e189a14e65a7ffecde5501b6c1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cb5fe8e189a14e65a7ffecde5501b6c1}" title="Nozawa Onsen">Nozawa village</a>, with a warm and welcoming Japanese service. The Onsen baths located on the top floor of the hotel with panoramic views of the village and mountains is an amazing place to finish your day on the slopes. The hotel is in a great location for exploring the village as well as being just a few minutes walk from the ski lifts. </p>
<p>This hotel is true to Japanese style, so expect a Japanese breakfast and showers and baths are available in the Onsen only.</p>
<p> </p>
